{"text_id":251396,"tokens":["Margin"," enlargement"," over"," training"," data"," has"," been"," an"," important"," strategy"," since"," percep","trons"," in"," machine"," learning"," for"," the"," purpose"," of"," boosting"," the"," robustness"," of"," classifiers"," toward"," a"," good"," generalization"," ability","."," Yet"," ,"," this"," is"," not"," always"," sufficient"," to"," achieve"," state","-","of","-","the","-","art"," performance"," and"," there"," are"," many"," applications"," where"," it"," would"," be"," desirable"," to"," have"," even"," higher"," robustness"," levels","."," One"," way"," to"," improve"," generalization"," error"," rate"," (","GER",")"," for"," marginal","-","en","larged"," classes"," is"," by"," using"," subspace"," methods"," [","1","]"," or"," various"," forms"," of"," nonlinear"," res","ampling"," such"," as"," linear"," subspace"," regression"," [","2","]."," However",","," these"," approaches"," often"," require"," the"," use"," of"," relatively"," large"," feature"," sizes"," which"," can"," result"," in"," inaccurate"," classification"," results"," due"," either"," to"," mis","specification"," or"," because"," costly"," rec","lassi","fy"," steps"," may"," become"," necessary"," in"," order"," to"," reduce"," the"," size"," of"," features"," used"," for"," classification","."," In"," contrast"," to"," traditional"," marginal","-","enhance","ment"," techniques"," that"," rely"," on"," very"," high"," accuracy",","," our"," work"," shows"," how"," marginal","-","enhancing"," techniques"," can"," be"," applied"," at"," lower"," acc","ura","cies"," with"," improved"," results"," when"," compared"," to"," pure"," marginal"," enhancement"," techniques"," without"," any"," other"," additional"," correction","."," The"," key"," contribution"," of"," this"," paper"," lies"," in"," combining"," two"," different"," dynamic"," programming"," algorithms",","," namely"," Lasso"," and"," Sub","regression",","," along"," with"," a"," nove